article_title: Former AIG Boss Hank Greenberg Bets On Obamacare

article_metadata.description: Maurice "Hank" Greenberg, who built AIG into an insurance powerhouse, bought medical claims processor MultiPlan for $4.4 billion from Silver Lake and BC Partners.
article_metadata.author: Zina Moukheiber
